Clusty
by Carl Mercier

-- Preliminary Release --

Easily start instances on EC2. See "config.rb" for configuration examples.

Syntax:

$ ./clusty-start {count} {cluster name} {instance name}

For example, start 1 database server like this:

$ ./clusty-start 1 cluster1 db

or start 10 web servers:

$ ./clusty-start 10 cluster1 web


Features:

  - Supports On Demand and Spot instances
  - Specify maximum Spot instance bid price
  - Supports user data
  
  